'''Pinacism''' was a religion that taught that individuals who did not interfere with [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] events should await a major [[Event]] after which the [[galactic community]] would fall apart. At that time, the Pinacists would be able to take control of the galaxy. The religion arose and despite the efforts of [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Malcom]], swept through [[Cmaoli Di/Legends|Cmaoli Di]] and then the rest of [[Brema sector/Legends|Brema sector]]. Its followers left in a great exodus to [[Kathol sector/Legends|Kathol sector]] where they founded the [[Pimbrellan League]] in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]].

